[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0985","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0985.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1156","title":"BisonWare FTP Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BisonWare FTP Server 4.1 及更早版本存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 FTP 服务的 PORT 命令发送包含非数字字符及大量回车符的恶意数据包，触发服务器崩溃或服务中断，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 BisonWare FTP Server 4.1 及之前的所有版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1156"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.407","remediation":"厂商 BisonWare 已停止运营，无官方补丁可用。建议立即升级到 BisonWare FTP Server 4.1 以上版本（如 5.0 或更高版本存在），或迁移至仍在维护的 FTP 服务器软件（如 FileZilla Server、ProFTPD 等）。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制 FTP 服务端口的访问来源 IP 范围，仅允许受信任网络连接，并在网络层部署入侵检测规则拦截格式异常的 PORT 命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2254"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0985.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1981","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1981.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1510","title":"BisonWare BisonFTP Server 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"BisonWare BisonFTP Server 4.1 之前版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务的 USER、LIST 或 CWD 命令发送超长字符串，触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致服务拒绝响应，甚至可执行任意代码。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，Metasploit 框架已集成对应的利用模块，风险较高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1510"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:35.723","remediation":"升级 BisonWare BisonFTP 服务器至 4.1 或更高版本以修复缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，在防火墙层面限制对 FTP 服务（默认端口 21）的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接，并禁用匿名用户写入权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92697301706956&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3234","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/17810"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1981.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0208","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0208.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0489","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 未信任脚本粘贴漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的 MSHTML.DLL 组件存在不可信脚本粘贴漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，利用脚本将用户本地文件路径粘贴至文件上传内建控件中，从而在用户无感知的情况下强制上传任意本地文件。该漏洞属于 MS98-013 公告所述\"不可信脚本粘贴\"问题的变种，攻击者无需任何用户交互即可窃取敏感文件。影响 Internet Explorer 5.0 及可能更早版本，CVSS v2.0 评分为 10.0，危害严重。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0489"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-17","updated":"1999-05-17","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-013 提供的补丁，将 mshtml.dll 升级至 4.72.3509.0100 及以上版本。对于 Windows 98 用户，通过 Windows Update 获取关键更新。对于已停止支持的旧系统，建议升级至受支持的 Windows 版本并使用现代浏览器，同时在 IE 中禁用活动脚本和跨域访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0208.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0208.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1082","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1082.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1366","title":"Pegasus 邮件客户端 POP3 密码弱加密存储漏洞","description":"Pegasus 电子邮件客户端 3.0 及更早版本存在密码存储加密强度不足漏洞。程序将 POP3 账户密码使用弱加密算法处理后明文或近似明文存储在 pmail.ini 配置文件中，本地攻击者只需访问该文件即可轻易解密获取密码，进而读取目标用户的电子邮件内容。该漏洞利用门槛低，无需特殊权限，属于本地信息泄露风险。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1366"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.223","remediation":"建议升级至 Pegasus Mail 3.1 及以上版本，该版本改进了 POP3 密码的加密存储方式。若无法升级，应限制对 pmail.ini 文件的本地访问权限，仅允许必要用户读取，并避免在多用户共享系统上使用该客户端处理敏感邮件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92714118829880&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1366.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1366","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1366.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1366.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h93v-m49q-355g/GHSA-h93v-m49q-355g.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1366.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000637.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/b929f4524cd5f55e84af4c34d9f33ee2512d5d4a/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--80679e4a-cea9-490e-88af-d157a83a5ea8.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1082.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0884","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0884.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1029","title":"SSH Communications Security sshd2 密码暴力破解漏洞","description":"SSH服务器sshd2 2.0.12之前版本存在认证记录缺失漏洞。当攻击者在达到最大尝试次数前主动关闭连接，服务端未能正确记录此次登录尝试，导致暴力破解行为不会出现在审计日志中。远程攻击者可利用此缺陷绕过审计机制，通过大量密码枚举尝试获取系统访问权限，严重影响系统安全性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1029"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.427","remediation":"升级 sshd2 至 2.0.12 或更高版本，该版本已正确记录所有登录尝试次数。同时可配置系统日志审计、部署 fail2ban 等暴力破解防护工具，并限制 SSH 登录尝试频率与来源 IP，增强暴力破解检测能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92663402004280&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/277","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2193","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1029","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1029.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6mfv-3x79-9r84/GHSA-6mfv-3x79-9r84.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/277/info.html","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-223.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0884.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0017","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0229","title":"Microsoft Windows NT IIS 目录遍历拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 服务器存在路径遍历拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送包含特殊构造的 `..\\..` 序列的 HTTP 请求触发目录遍历，导致服务器资源耗尽或崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统上的 Microsoft IIS 服务，利用方式简单，危害性较高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0229"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.530","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本（含 IIS 5.0+），或在 Windows NT 4.0 上安装 IIS 4.0 Service Pack 及 MS98-004 安全补丁。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中禁用未使用的虚拟目录并移除可执行权限以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0229","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0229","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0229.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79m3-vm8c-387r/GHSA-79m3-vm8c-387r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_crash.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2218/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0229.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0017.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0507","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0507.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0776","title":"阿里巴巴 HTTP Server 路径遍历漏洞","description":"阿里巴巴 HTTP 服务器存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送包含 `../` 序列的特制 HTTP 请求，突破路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞源于服务器对用户请求路径过滤不严，未正确处理 `..` 路径回溯符，攻击者可利用此漏洞获取敏感配置文件或系统文件，导致信息泄露。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0776"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:02.090","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的阿里巴巴 HTTP 服务器，迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx 等仍在积极维护的 Web 服务器软件。在迁移完成前，可在 Web 服务器前端部署反向代理或 WAF，配置规则拦截包含 `..` 的 URL 请求路径作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9905&L=NTBUGTRAQ&P=R1533"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0507.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1084","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1084.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1368","title":"Computer Associates InoculateIT MS Exchange Server 选项病毒绕过检测漏洞","description":"InoculateIT 4.53 及可能其他版本的 MS Exchange Server 防病毒选项仅扫描 Microsoft Exchange 服务器的收件箱文件夹树，当用户邮件规则将邮件移动到其他邮箱时，病毒可绕过检测。攻击者利用此设计缺陷，通过将含病毒邮件移出收件箱即可逃避扫描，导致系统被感染。该漏洞影响 InoculateIT 4.53 及可能更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1368"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.480","remediation":"升级 InoculateIT 至 4.53 以上版本，确保 AV 选项配置为扫描所有 Exchange 邮箱文件夹而非仅收件箱。如厂商已停止支持，建议迁移至其他支持全邮箱扫描的防病毒方案（如 Microsoft Defender for Office 365），并禁用自动移动邮件的用户规则作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92652152723629&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=97439568517355&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1368.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1368","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1368.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1368.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qgqh-3fh5-37xc/GHSA-qgqh-3fh5-37xc.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1368.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000635.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9186387f-2fa8-40f8-814b-8ce0daf4dc95.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1084.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0514","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0514.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0785","title":"ISC INN inndstart 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"ISC INN (InterNetNews) 新闻服务器软件中的 inndstart 程序存在权限管理缺陷，由于未对 inn.conf 配置文件中的 \"pathrun\" 参数进行充分校验，本地攻击者可通过构造恶意的 pathrun 路径参数，使 inndstart 以 root 权限执行任意程序，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 ISC INN 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本或严格限制 inn.conf 文件的写入权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0785"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.197","remediation":"升级 ISC INN 至 2.2.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 inndstart 对 pathrun 参数的不安全处理。如无法升级，确保 inn.conf 中 pathrun 指向受保护目录（如 /usr/local/news/bin），且该目录仅允许 root 用户写入，同时移除 inndstart 的 setuid root 权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/254"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0514.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0514.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0887","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0887.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1033","title":"Microsoft Outlook Express POP3 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook Express 4.72.3612.1700 之前版本存在 POP3 协议处理缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含特殊构造的 \"..\" 字符串的恶意邮件，诱使 Outlook 重新进入 POP3 命令模式，导致 POP3 会话挂起无法继续处理后续邮件，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Outlook Express 4.27.3110 及 4.72.3120 等版本，攻击者无需认证即可触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1033"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.953","remediation":"将 Microsoft Outlook Express 升级至 4.72.3612.1700 或更高版本，此版本修复了包含 \"..\" 序列的恶意邮件导致 POP3 命令模式循环挂起的问题。如无法升级，建议禁用 POP3 邮箱功能或改用 IMAP 协议收信作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92647407427342&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92663402004275&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/252","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19207","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1033.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1033","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/xaitax/SploitScan/blob/e7c7a6140bbd6a60ea622b6124620fbed9d12332/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1033.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-935q-jf44-fq38/GHSA-935q-jf44-fq38.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0887.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0501","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0773","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 lpset 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 系统中的 lpset 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可通过向该程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的关键数据，成功利用此漏洞可获得 root 权限，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低，危害严重。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0773"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-11","updated":"1999-05-11","remediation":"升级 Sun Solaris 至 7.0 及以上补丁版本，或迁移至受支持的 Solaris 8/9/10 版本。如无法升级，建议限制 /usr/bin/lpset 的 setuid 权限（chmod 0500 /usr/bin/lpset）并移除不必要的用户对 lpset 的执行权限作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19206","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0773.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0773","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0773.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0773.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p7vf-vpjm-9fh3/GHSA-p7vf-vpjm-9fh3.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0773.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3b243205-0c36-4aa3-9d0c-556bbfd3e3f1.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd2a79eb3e801a346d1f2affda8f984b2830c654/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0608","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0608.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0754","title":"ISC INN 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"INN（InterNetNews）新闻服务器的 inndstart 程序存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置 INNCONF 环境变量指定恶意配置文件，使 inndstart 以提升的权限加载并执行该配置，从而获取系统更高权限。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版中的 INN 软件包，攻击者利用此漏洞可完全控制受影响系统。厂商已发布安全补丁进行修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0754"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-11","updated":"1999-05-11","remediation":"升级 INN 至 2.2.2 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可移除 inndstart 程序的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/inndstart），阻止普通用户通过 INNCONF 环境变量加载恶意配置文件提权。同时限制对 INN 配置目录的写入权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0754.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0754.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0754","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0754.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0754.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-c5pf-965c-g6g8/GHSA-c5pf-965c-g6g8.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/255/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0754.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0608.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0568","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0806","title":"Sun Solaris dtprintinfo 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 系统中的 dtprintinfo 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，该程序位于 /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo，在处理特制输入时未正确验证缓冲区边界，导致可被利用覆盖内存数据。本地攻击者可通过向 dtprintinfo 传递超长参数触发溢出，进而以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，需本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0806"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.767","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 107080-01（SPARC 平台）或 107081-01（x86 平台）修复 dtprintinfo 缓冲区溢出漏洞。若无法打补丁，立即移除 dtprintinfo 的 setuid 位：chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo，或限制仅管理员可执行：chmod 700 /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo。如不需要 CDE 打印功能可直接删除该二进制文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6552","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19205"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0245","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0245.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0686","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server HP-UX 平台长 URL 请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server（NES）在 HP-UX 平台的 HP Virtual Vault（VVOS）环境中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制超长 URL 请求，触发服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，导致服务器无法正常处理合法用户请求。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击门槛较低，主要影响 HP Virtual Vault 操作系统上运行的 NES Web 服务，在特定网络条件下可造成拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0686"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.783","remediation":"建议立即升级 Netscape Enterprise Server 至 3.6 SP2 及以上版本（HP-UX 对应安全补丁编号 PHSS_20316）。在反向代理或负载均衡器（如 HP-UX Apache-based Web Server）上限制 URL 长度不超过 4096 字节，拒绝超过阈值的请求。配置 WAF 规则过滤包含超长路径的 HTTP 请求。由于 NES 及 HP-UX Virtual Vault 均已停止技术支持，长期解决方案应迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server）和操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-046.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9906-098","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0686","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0686.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrj2-v329-4cm9/GHSA-mrj2-v329-4cm9.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0245.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0245.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0316","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0316.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0717","title":"Microsoft Excel 97 病毒警告机制绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Excel 97 的病毒警告机制存在安全缺陷，远程攻击者可通过构造特制的 Excel 文件或利用特定方式触发该漏洞，绕过或禁用 Excel 内置的病毒警告功能，导致用户在不知情的情况下打开包含宏病毒的文件。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 97 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级较低，CVSS 评分 2.6。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0717"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.573","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft Office 2000 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，建议在 Excel 97 中启用宏安全级别为「高」，并仅打开来自可信来源的 Excel 文件，同时安装 Microsoft 发布的 Office 97 SR-2 安全更新。此外，建议部署防病毒软件并配置为扫描所有 Office 文档附件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231304","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-014","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0717.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0717","https://github.com/cv